{"tid":246414,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[湧fans]睇住湧士贏波完全冇開心嘅感覺","createTime":"2017-05-17T03:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T07:03:04.000Z","uid":91947,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f36fadc8c6987902b8fee3db3f7b32ae3406a78","tid":246414,"uid":91947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:46:58.000Z","msg":"由Ellis船長Davis開始留意湧士<br />\n一手一腳養起自己pick嘅新秀<br />\nBarns, Green, KT<br />\nCurry用技術由underdog打到MVP級數<br />\n完全係最憎嘅占士嘅相反<br />\n唔係靠天份體能crybaby插水組團金錢籃球<br />\n<br />\n到後來Gentry嚟左，引入太陽打法再昇華<br />\n仲帶埋個人最愛嘅Barbosa嚟<br />\n作為太陽忠心fans，就因為咁而真係開始鍾意湧<br />\n加埋生命石O'neal Lee Bogut一堆生涯救贖嘅老將<br />\n期待佢地將太陽嘅Run and Gun加快樂團隊籃球打低占士<br />\n點知幾round對家主力傷晒，騎又傷兩個主力<br />\n一直唔能夠打對家full team嚟證明自己<br />\n<br />\n第二年打到73-9, 大好機會兩隊full team打<br />\n但到季尾為破紀錄搏太盡<br />\nCurry又傷，隊波冇左季中嗰種節奏<br />\n到finals 3-1嗰陣，bogut 2姑又傷<br />\n就算green之前起腳，但占士跨嗰下Green根本冇flagrant foul<br />\n但又俾占士叫nba禁左佢賽<br />\n隊波開始亂，打西波，俾73-9唔輸得嘅壓力食返自己<br />\n加加埋埋咁就俾騎反cup<br />\n好唔忿氣輸俾金錢籃球<br />\n都算，俾籍口自己話一人一年傷主力當打和<br />\n<br />\n好期待今年兩隊full team打過<br />\n但留唔住barns，仲走去簽durant<br />\n雖然冇錢留barns走去簽durant好合理<br />\n但即刻搞臭隊波，仲一走走晒一班14年功臣<br />\n賭撚又唔撚識夾隊波，成日單打<br />\n好地地一隊兄弟波走左個外人on9仔嚟<br />\n每日都剩係想賭撚快啲走即刻走<br />\n俾Curry佢地原本嘅人證明自己<br />\n<br />\n終於今年打馬刺，兩隊都打teamwork、都好鍾意<br />\nKawhi, Simmons又係underdog打到KO占士<br />\n好期待<br />\n<br />\n點知<br />\n<img src=\"https://usatftw.files.wordpress.com/2017/05/screen-shot-2017-05-14-at-5-41-48-pm.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=600&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusatftw.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fscreen-shot-2017-05-14-at-5-41-48-pm.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D600%26crop%3D1&h=dd7327c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個Series咁就搞臭晒<br />\n而家贏幾多都唔會開心<br />\n<br />\n或者可能賭撚走左，先可以真正替湧拎冠覺得開心"},{"pid":"563471574b50bacc55aa170c332d0bfd7cb67347","tid":246414,"uid":91947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"幾開心嗰陣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8chwpun1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8chwpun1&h=c4a3b658&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9698171c892a59fb9aeb72b5db5dbc7dd4e209d6","tid":246414,"uid":9217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"反刺唔會理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65edcbddd236674aa017640a29302c011b16d85d","tid":246414,"uid":91947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反刺唔會理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n波波老謀深算發下火激起隊波嘅怒氣同外界嘅壓力<br />\n等可愛返嚟湧就仆街了"},{"pid":"e8a1f50344eee98fc8ec565eb5e206365bcaffe7","tid":246414,"uid":34876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"刺狗咪一樣咁zip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懶感性"},{"pid":"c2c8f91373a2c2c0260dc544f9f98e7ddd759d97","tid":246414,"uid":6070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"簽唔簽kd班bench都走架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f1fdccf3cc05af6e1ca9b90bc02cd381f4e6ab","tid":246414,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"今年D助攻好似創新高喎... 樓主有無睇波架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297908ce3c42b7a62d01b11293919b75bc7b01c1","tid":246414,"uid":91947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簽唔簽kd班bench都走架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBench嚟講，唔簽賭撚咪有錢簽<br />\n但要bench定賭撚，咪話最後簽賭撚好合理<br />\n<br />\n係唔鍾意佢姐"},{"pid":"5db58a372e00cbe0bf991708bdfd34b1e5d0a79b","tid":246414,"uid":91947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score